Class IKResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brashmonkey.spriter.IKResolver
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CCDResolver

    public abstract class IKResolver
extends java.lang.Object
    A IKResolver is responsible for resolving previously set constraints.

        Parameters:
        x - the target x value
        y - the target y value
        chainLength - number of parents which are affected
